folder: Gouverneur Street & Front Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
View 1:
Gouverneur Street, Front to South Street, showing R.R. piers of the N.Y. and New Haven R.R.

View 2:
Gouverneur Street; from Water Street, looking north showing clearing between Cherry and Monroe Street.

P.L. Speer
September 18, 1939.
